snippet.title: Best VGM 703 - Michael Jackson's Moonwalker - Billie Jean (Caverns)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Sega Genesis
Michael Jackson's Moonwalker (1990)
Billie Jean (Caverns)
Michael Jackson & Hiroshi Kubota
